{"tid":837913,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個接近死亡嘅時刻","createTime":"2018-09-26T17:21:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-27T00:08:52.000Z","uid":212459,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9fe398a3313a9da3595728f4f7e50425064cb142","tid":837913,"uid":212459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T17:21:38.000Z","msg":"細個去唔知乜鬼水上樂園<br />\n唔知邊到黎嘅膽去玩造浪池<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嗰時人仔細細 唔識游水又冇著救生衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n池水應該啱啱到我頸左右<br />\n<br />\n本身玩得好地地<br />\n點知個池越黎越多人 個浪越黎越高<br />\n最後我對腳完全掂唔到池底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我不斷掙扎<br />\n但我嗌救命又完全嗌唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個鼻吸曬啲水好撚辛苦<br />\n嗰陣個腦一片空白 以為自己真係係咁先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後好彩有救生員見到跳落黎救我<br />\n救翻我一命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c325a44d82347b7c4b8576be8625240168b1a88f","tid":837913,"uid":22974,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T17:29:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f015f1e507c5ab72f7feb2486b73a57abc1196ea","tid":837913,"uid":206344,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T17:29:44.000Z","msg":"有次同個唔識遊水嘅fd  岀到浮台同沙灘嘅中間點<br />\n之後佢原本坐定定喺浮床上面  <br />\n但無啦啦碌撚咗落水 <br />\n仲要攬住我不斷掙扎 <br />\n我不斷用力踩水  但個人一直沉<br />\n最尾我一手捉浮床同另一個fd拉起佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbd1f55348a19ccca81d14a392f33368ce1dfc47","tid":837913,"uid":205773,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T17:31:30.000Z","msg":"我成日懷疑啲泳灘泳池咁多人啲救生係咪真係咁好眼力睇到你出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"777a3c2f3e6c528d617fbdbf47c07dc79ada0c4d","tid":837913,"uid":205773,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T17:31:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我成日懷疑啲泳灘泳池咁多人啲救生員係咪真係咁好眼力睇到你出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"97af9467c3401e9fa9f155a4ac2ef59e678caedc","tid":837913,"uid":37971,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T17:31:56.000Z","msg":"喺屋企插電掣同遙控車電池個叉機駁電<br />\n冇留意個插頭着咗掣<br />\n一插插頭<br />\n見到好光好明顯嘅電光出現0.1秒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嗰吓覺得同死亡嘅距離就係差嗰大約1cm"},{"pid":"bef67604536cedadeaf21b142a5a8c285a2fecdd","tid":837913,"uid":90244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f015f1e507c5ab72f7feb2486b73a57abc1196ea","tid":837913,"uid":206344,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T17:29:44.000Z","msg":"有次同個唔識遊水嘅fd  岀到浮台同沙灘嘅中間點<br />\n之後佢原本坐定定喺浮床上面  <br />\n但無啦啦碌撚咗落水 <br />\n仲要攬住我不斷掙扎 <br />\n我不斷用力踩水  但個人一直沉<br />\n最尾我一手捉浮床同另一個fd拉起佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T17:32:41.000Z","msg":"唔識游水 出咁深水就抵死啦"},{"pid":"c380dbc4fa25785874d1fd5fed03a0ac432bc9d5","tid":837913,"uid":206344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bef67604536cedadeaf21b142a5a8c285a2fecdd","tid":837913,"uid":90244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f015f1e507c5ab72f7feb2486b73a57abc1196ea","tid":837913,"uid":206344,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T17:29:44.000Z","msg":"有次同個唔識遊水嘅fd  岀到浮台同沙灘嘅中間點<br />\n之後佢原本坐定定喺浮床上面  <br />\n但無啦啦碌撚咗落水 <br />\n仲要攬住我不斷掙扎 <br />\n我不斷用力踩水  但個人一直沉<br />\n最尾我一手捉浮床同另一個fd拉起佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T17:32:41.000Z","msg":"唔識游水 出咁深水就抵死啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-